---
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>SnapProtein Blog</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Evidence-based articles on protein, muscle, and healthy aging."
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --charcoal: #1e2124;
        --green: #3a6b45;
        --green-light: #4d8c5a;
        --cream: #f9f6f0;
        --text: #1e2124;
        --text-muted: #5a6370;
        --border: #d8dde3;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--cream);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .site-header {
        background: var(--charcoal);
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .site-header a.logo {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .site-header a.logo span {
        color: var(--green-light);
      }

      .site-header nav a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 1.25rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .site-header nav a:hover {
        color: white;
      }

      .hero {
        background: var(--charcoal);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .hero p {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 680px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .wrap {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      }

      .post-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }

      .post-card {
        background: white;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .post-card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .post-card h2 a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .post-card h2 a:hover {
        color: var(--green);
      }

      .post-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      footer {
        background: var(--charcoal);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a href="https://snapprotein.com" class="logo">Snap<span>Protein</span></a>
      <nav>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
        <a href="https://snapprotein.com/#app">Try the App</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>SnapProtein Blog</h1>
      <p>
        Straightforward articles on protein, muscle, healthy aging, and why most
        men over 50 need more protein than they think.
      </p>
    </section>

    <main class="wrap">
      <div class="post-list">
        <article class="post-card">
          <h2>
            <a href="/blog/protein-after-50/">
              How Much Protein Do Men Over 50 Need?
            </a>
          </h2>
          <p>
            Most men over 50 are eating far less protein than they actually need.
            Here’s what the science says — and the simplest way to fix it.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="post-card">
  <h2>
    <a href="/blog/muscle-loss-after-40/">
      Why You're Losing Muscle After 40
    </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    If you're over 40 and losing strength despite working out, the problem isn't your effort. Here's the real reason — and what actually fixes it.
  </p>
</article>

<article class="post-card">
  <h2>
    <a href="/blog/myfitnesspal-alternative/">
      MyFitnessPal Is Great. It’s Also Way Too Complicated After 40.
    </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    MyFitnessPal is a powerful app, but for men over 40 who only need to hit a protein target, its complexity creates more friction than value.
  </p>
</article>

<article class="post-card">
  <h2>
    <a href="/blog/high-protein-foods-after-50/">
      Best High-Protein Foods After 50 (Simple, No Cooking Required)
    </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    The easiest high-protein foods for men over 50 — no meal prep, no complicated recipes, no chef skills required.
  </p>
</article>

<article class="post-card">
  <h2>
    <a href="/blog/30-gram-protein-rule/">
      Best High-Protein Foods After 50 (Simple, No Cooking Required)
    </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    The easiest high-protein foods for men over 50 — no meal prep, no complicated recipes, no chef skills required.
  </p>
</article>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © 2025 SnapProtein
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>